

Build all libraries and firmware
================================

build_firmware.sh - build for Broadcom SoC's (Raspberry Pi, minimum support)
build_h3-firmware.sh - build for Allwinner SoC's H2+/H3 (OrangePi Zero & OrangePi One)
build_linux.sh - build for host PC (debugging)
build_circle.sh  -  (not sure)

Assistants - Please read / modify these script files...
=======================================================

build_this.sh 
- used to build one H3 firmware from it's directory and optionally upload it, edit to specify IP address
- eg ./opi_emac_ltc_smpte$ ../scripts/build_this.sh 

do-tftp.sh
- upload to device via tftp, edit to select upload to either Opi Zero or Opi One

Used by build scripts
=====================
libs-clean.sh 
makeall_circle-lib.sh
makeall_circle.sh
makeall_firmware_h3-lib.sh
makeall_firmware_h3.sh
makeall_firmware-lib.sh
makeall_firmware.sh
makeall_linux-lib.sh
makeall_linux.sh
